data.description: Welcome to this stunning home situated in the Trails at Crowfoot neighborhood in the beautiful town of Parker. No need to wait for construction; move in now and get a DR Horton home built in 2022. Inside, you'll be greeted by a welcoming open-concept floor plan, and the kitchen comes with stainless steel appliances, a gas range, quartz counters, and a spacious island.  This is a 4 beds 3 baths home and laundry room is upstairs where all the bedrooms are.  Spacious 3 car garage provides ample space.  Work from home is made easy from the main level office. Just outside the walk-out basement is a landscaped backyard, perfect for enjoying warm summer days and hosting gatherings. Beautiful views of the plains from the deck on the main level.  South-facing driveway makes snow removal a breeze.  Additionally, this home features LVP flooring throughout the main floor, smart home features such as thermostats,garage doors,video camera,door bell that are controlled by an app. This property is located within the highly acclaimed Douglas County School District, known for its excellent education and commitment to student success.  The upcoming Leman Academy is being built in the neighborhood and is anticipated for students in Fall of 2024, providing additional educational opportunities. Residents of this home will also enjoy access to a plethora of nearby amenities, including the renowned Trails Great Park. This park offers great recreational activities, including a baseball field, a multi-use field, a playground area with shade structures, 3 tennis courts that can be converted to 12 pickleball courts, a full basketball court, a pool, a looped trail, and a 9-hole disc golf course, ensuring fun for all. Close to I-25/C470, DTC, park and ride, and the RTD light rail. The Pace Center, Main Street Parker (shops/restaurants), Library, Parker Ice Trail at Discovery Park, and a dog park. Don't miss the chance to own this amazing property in Parker. This will not last long! 720-949-5450
